This paper deals with the problem of optimizing the coding rates for distributed averaging in a network, which involves information theory, control systems, machine learning, and networking. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IT (Information Theory), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
